description: Garlic Scapes a gourmet style food truck that is centered around garlic. Garlic scapes are the shoots that garlic bulbs continuously sprout as they grow. If you love garlic you will love our food. We are based out of Orange County and travel far and wide to get you the best food you can imagine.Like garlic scapes, we also continue to grow and weave through this journey of life. We hope that your growth leads you to enjoy many moments with those you love, and who love you.
name: Garlic Scapes
